{"tid":203900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁繼昌被拒入境澳門","createTime":"2017-04-16T15:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T15:52:05.000Z","uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e751de2b22d9418745944508d381e436c25e89ec","tid":203900,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:39:46.000Z","msg":"梁繼昌打算今日與家人到澳門旅遊，但中午到達澳門使用電子通道入境不成功，其後被帶到一房間內逾半小時，他引述澳門當局指強烈懷疑他會「從事危害公共安全或公共秩序的活動」，而拒絕讓他入境，但未有解釋詳情。梁繼昌曾提出上訴，並展示租住酒店的單據，強調此行是純粹旅遊及消費，但最終仍未拒入境，約一小時後乘船返港。<br />\n<br />\n梁繼昌表示，早前曾成功到佛山旅遊及到東江流域考察，以往皆可出入澳門，上次到訪澳門為去年4月，故對今次被拒入境感到困惑及不滿，質疑是否所有民主派議員都不能入境澳門。他又指，已向香港保安局局長及候任行政長官林鄭月娥反映事件，要求跟進。"},{"pid":"38fdd2214352a6a3c9e38c7f063207549bf6087c","tid":203900,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:43:20.000Z","msg":"返到支那但去唔到澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0d8a116ab3ac373e1943869fc088b85e847979","tid":203900,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:44:39.000Z","msg":"澳豬真係on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab8ccdb0f6b7e928778d39ca82c8257f5f54cab","tid":203900,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返到支那但去唔到澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請勿用個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>返</strong></span>字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194ffe79d9681d57713198133f5d6329a90aaaf1","tid":203900,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:51:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2430e52e9e4b21a9b40d490ee81170dde794146f","tid":203900,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,